37:04.431 --> 37:05.762
PLEASE...

37:05.849 --> 37:07.214
PLEASE?

37:09.644 --> 37:11.976
LISTEN TO ME, PETER,

37:12.063 --> 37:14.976
AND LET THEM LISTEN.

37:15.066 --> 37:17.774
OR ELSE I'LL TELL THEM
ABOUT A QUAKING, WHIMPERING BOY

37:17.861 --> 37:20.148
WHO CRIED ON MY COUCH;

37:20.238 --> 37:22.354
WHO STILL CRIES ON MY COUCH.

37:22.449 --> 37:25.487
[whispering]: PLEASE DON'T.
PLEASE, ERNST, PLEASE DON'T.

37:25.577 --> 37:28.319
DON'T LET HIM DO THIS.
PUT HIM DOWN. PUT HIM DOWN.

37:28.413 --> 37:31.781
YEAH, PUT ME DOWN,
PUT ME DOWN. SHUT ME UP!

37:31.875 --> 37:34.367
STIFLE ME-- WHY DON'T YOU?

37:34.461 --> 37:36.293
[quieter]: WHY CAN'T YOU?

37:38.465 --> 37:42.003
BECAUSE THIS IS
YOUR COURAGE RIGHT HERE.

37:42.093 --> 37:44.380
