AND THE CROWD,

37:50.101 --> 37:51.182
<i>AND THE SIEG HEIL!</i>

37:51.269 --> 37:52.475
[slaps]

37:52.562 --> 37:54.144
[shocked murmurs]

37:59.903 --> 38:01.769
THE REBUTTAL.

38:03.698 --> 38:06.690
