YOUR KIND KNOWS HOW TO GIVE.

38:12.290 --> 38:14.122
THIS IS YOUR FUHRER.

38:16.920 --> 38:19.628
HE'S YOURS.

38:19.714 --> 38:21.330
I GIVE HIM TO YOU.

38:23.718 --> 38:26.130
A GIFT FROM THE SEWERS.

38:50.954 --> 38:52.536
Man: MR. VOLLMER.

39:06.970 --> 39:08.881
YOU SEE...

39:08.972 --> 39:11.509
THE WAY IT IS?

