39:15.979 --> 39:21.270
IS THAT A FACT, MR. VOLLMER?

39:21.359 --> 39:24.897
FOR SUCH A LONG TIME.

39:24.988 --> 39:28.902
I'VE KNOWN HIM FOR SO LONG.

39:28.992 --> 39:30.699
I'VE KNOWN HIM FOR SO LONG.

39:30.785 --> 39:32.696
HE CHEAPENED YOU, MR. VOLLMER.

39:32.787 --> 39:35.279
HE TORE YOU TO PIECES!

39:35.373 --> 39:37.705
YOUR VOICE IS THAT OF A LION,

39:37.792 --> 39:40.079
