ARE THOSE OF A RABBIT.

39:40.169 --> 39:41.546
AND YOU--

39:41.629 --> 39:43.916
WHAT ARE YOU?!

39:44.007 --> 39:46.715
YOU DIRECT TRAFFIC
FROM THE DARKNESS!

39:46.801 --> 39:50.169
YOU PLAN THE BATTLES, AND YOU'RE
NE\/ER THERE VVHEN THEY'RE FOUGHT!

39:50.263 --> 39:53.847
