ALONGSIDE OF ME?

39:57.353 --> 40:00.141
WHY DON'T YOU GIVE ME A NAME...

40:00.231 --> 40:01.938
AND A FACE...

40:02.025 --> 40:04.016
AND A REASON WHY?

40:04.110 --> 40:06.522
MR. VOLLMER.

40:06.613 --> 40:09.947
I WAS MAKING SPEECHES
BEFORE YOU COULD READ THEM.

40:10.033 --> 40:11.774
I WAS FIGHTING BATTLES

40:11.868 --> 40:15.953
WHEN YOUR ONLY STRUGGLE
WAS TO CLIMB OUT OF A WOMB.

40:16.039 --> 40:18.326
I WAS TAKING OVER THE WORLD

40:18.416 --> 40:21.750
WHEN YOUR UNIVERSE WAS A CRIB!

40:21.836 --> 40:25.170
AND AS FOR BEING IN DARKNESS,
MR. VOLLMER,

40:25.256 --> 40:27.668
I INVENTED DARKNESS!

40:32.639 --> 40:37.258
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

40:42.065 --> 40:44.306
[gasps]

41:18.351 --> 41:20.513
[panting]

41:20.603 --> 41:24.597
YOU... YOU PICKED ME.

41:24.691 --> 41:26.147
YOU PICKED ME.

41:29.112 --> 41:32.321
I DID NOT PICK YOU, MR. VOLLMER.
YOU PIOKED ME.

41:32.407 --> 41:35.365
YOU CHOSE MY IDEAS,

41:35.451 --> 41:38.534
YOU INVOKED MY NAME,
YOU STOLE MY SLOGANS.

41:38.621 --> 41:41.113
SO NOW, YOU MUST TAKE
WHATEVER ELSE COMES WITH IT.

41:41.207 --> 41:45.041
IN THE PAST,
I HAVE GIVEN YOU SUGGESTIONS.

41:45.128 --> 41:46.869
NOW I GIVE ORDERS!

41:46.963 --> 41:50.627
AND FROM NOW ON,
YOU MUST BE BUILT OF STEEL.

41:50.717 --> 41:52.833
STEEL, MR. VOLLMER.

41:52.927 --> 41:55.419
NO SOFT GAPS OF SENTIMENT.

41:55.513 --> 41:57.299
LIKE WE HANDLED NICK.

41:57.390 --> 42:00.428
LIKE WE HANDLED THE MOBS.
LIKE WE MADE THE SPEECHES.

42:00.518 --> 42:03.431
AND BIT BY BIT, GRADUALLY,

42:03.521 --> 42:06.058
WE SHALL FORGE A FORCE--

42:06.149 --> 42:10.438
FIRST AN IDEA, THEN A FORCE.

42:10.528 --> 42:13.270
JUST AS I DID IT BEFORE,
MR. VOLLMER,

42:13.364 --> 42:15.446
WITH MY OWN HANDS!

42:15.533 --> 42:17.524
WITH MY OWN HANDS!

42:19.746 --> 42:24.456
THE OLD MAN, THE JEW,
HE'LL BE BACK AGAIN,

42:24.542 --> 42:28.080
TOMORROW NIGHT, THE NEXT NIGHT.
I KNOW HIM, I KNOW THE TYPE.

42:28.171 --> 42:30.458
WE SENT THEM INTO THE OVENS,
BUT ALWAYS,

42:30.548 --> 42:33.461
THERE WAS A HANDFUL LEFT
TO POINT A FINGER.

42:33.551 --> 42:35.087
HIS KIND, MR. VOLLMER,

42:35.178 --> 42:37.465
HIS KIND ARE DANGEROUS.

42:37.555 --> 42:41.890
THEY TALK, THEY THINK,
THEY PLANT A SEED.

42:41.976 --> 42:43.637
THEY HOLD US BACK!

42:46.981 --> 42:48.437
KILL HIM!

42:48.524 --> 42:50.140
KILL THE OLD MAN!

42:53.196 --> 42:55.528
KILL HIM? KILL ERNST?

42:55.615 --> 42:57.822
YES, TONIGHT. NOW.

42:57.909 --> 42:59.900
HE'LL BE IN HIS ROOM.

42:59.994 --> 43:02.907
ALL RIGHT, I'LL DO IT.

43:02.997 --> 43:04.738
I'LL DO IT RIGHT NOW.

43:12.590 --> 43:14.581
AND MR. VOLLMER...

43:14.675 --> 43:18.509
WHEN YOU COME BACK,
WE WILL HAVE MUCH TO TALK ABOUT.

43:18.596 --> 43:21.133
PLANS, CAMPAIGNS, lDEAS--

43:21.224 --> 43:23.010
THE FIRST STEPS.

43:23.101 --> 43:26.469
THIS IS ONLY THE BEGINNING,
MR. VOLLMER.

43:26.562 --> 43:29.520
THIS IS JUST THE DAWN.

43:29.607 --> 43:35.023
IT WILL BE A LONG, LONG DAY!

43:35.113 --> 43:37.605
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

43:41.702 --> 43:43.568
YOU WOULDN'T LISTEN TO ME,
ERNST.

43:43.663 --> 43:45.449
YOU WOULDN'T PAY ATTENTION.

43:45.540 --> 43:47.747
ON THE CONTRARY.

43:47.834 --> 43:49.996
I LISTENED TO YOU
ALL I COULD STAND.

43:50.086 --> 43:53.750
I COULDN'T EVEN BEGIN TO TELL
YOU WHAT'S HAPPENED, ERNST.

43:53.840 --> 43:56.753
IT'S TOO INCREDIBLE,
TOO UNBELIEVABLE.

43:56.843 --> 43:58.299
THERE'S NO STOPPING US NOW.

43:58.386 --> 44:01.754
NO STOPPING YOU, PETER.

44:01.848 --> 44:06.388
AN OLD MAN STOPPED YOU TONIGHT,
WITH A FEW WORDS.

44:06.477 --> 44:08.639
HE STOPPED YOU WITH THE TRUTH.

44:08.688 --> 44:11.555
NO, YOU'RE WRONG, ERNST.

44:11.649 --> 44:13.981
IT'S NOT JUST ME ANYMORE.

44:14.068 --> 44:16.560
THERE'S SOMEONE ELSE BEHIND US.

44:16.654 --> 44:18.565
SOMEONE THAT YOU'D TREMBLE AT.

44:18.656 --> 44:21.990
HE'D HAVE TO BE
A VERY IMPOSING FIGURE, PETER.

44:22.076 --> 44:23.942
MORE IMPOSING THAN YOU.

44:33.671 --> 44:36.083
MORE IMPOSING
THAN THAT, TOO, PETER.

44:36.174 --> 44:39.587
THAT'S ONLY BECAUSE
YOU DON'T THINK I'LL USE IT.

44:39.677 --> 44:42.385
WHICH SHOWS YOU DON'T KNOW ME
VERY WELL, ERNST.

44:42.471 --> 44:45.213
I KNOW YOU, PETER.

44:45.308 --> 44:48.016
I KNOW YOU.

44:48.102 --> 44:51.595
FROM A RAVAGED LITTLE BOY
WANTING LOVE...

44:51.689 --> 44:54.602
TO A TORN MAN

44:54.692 --> 44:58.902
CRAVING RESPECT,
IDENTITY, PRIDE.

45:01.699 --> 45:04.817
PETER... I DON'T FEAR YOU,

45:04.911 --> 45:10.122
SO YOU MAY DO VVHAT YOU HA\/E
IN MIND AT ANY TIME YOU VVISH.

45:10.208 --> 45:13.701
FOR THIS LAST ONE REMINDER
TO YOU.

45:16.130 --> 45:20.044
YOU CAN NEVER KILL AN IDEA
WITH A BULLET, PETER.

45:20.134 --> 45:21.716
NEVER.

45:24.555 --> 45:27.638
I'M ALL STEEL NOW.

45:27.725 --> 45:30.057
ERNST, I'M MADE OF STEEL.

45:30.144 --> 45:34.058
NO SENTIMENT, NO SOFTNESS.

45:34.148 --> 45:35.855
JUST PURPOSE AND WILL.

45:35.942 --> 45:38.855
THEN SHOOT.

45:38.945 --> 45:40.481
KILL.

45:40.571 --> 45:42.232
DESTROY ME.

45:47.912 --> 45:50.904
<i>[dramatic music plays]</i>

45:53.960 --> 45:56.292
[groans]

45:56.379 --> 45:59.497
ALL STEEL...

45:59.590 --> 46:01.752
ALL STRENGTH.

46:04.387 --> 46:07.800
BUT AT THE EXPENSE OF THE THING
MOST OTHER MEN HAVE.

46:09.600 --> 46:14.515
SOME... FRAGMENTS OF DECENCY

46:14.605 --> 46:16.391
TO TELL THEM RIGHT FROM WRONG...

46:16.482 --> 46:18.723
[coughs]

46:21.904 --> 46:24.521
MAKE THEM FEEL GUILT
AT DISHONOR...

46:26.993 --> 46:28.449
THAT MAKE THEM...

46:31.205 --> 46:33.037
...THAT MAKE THEM LOVE.

46:35.710 --> 46:39.544
YES, PETER...

46:39.630 --> 46:41.621
YOU HAVE STEEL...

46:44.802 --> 46:47.419
...BUT YOU HAVE NO HEART.

47:23.007 --> 47:24.998
<i>Hitler: MR. VOLLMER!</i>

47:27.053 --> 47:29.044
<i>SENTIMENTALITY?</i>

47:36.687 --> 47:38.018
NONE.

47:38.105 --> 47:40.767
<i>STEEL TONIGHT?</i>

47:40.858 --> 47:42.394
STEEL.

47:42.485 --> 47:45.603
<i>AND NO REGRETS?</i>

47:45.696 --> 47:47.027
NONE.

47:47.114 --> 47:49.572
<i>WHAT DID YOU DESTROY TONIGHT?</i>

47:49.658 --> 47:52.787
ONLY A DISEASE.

47:52.870 --> 47:55.953
A GROWTH THAT WAS ON OUR FLESH
THAT HAD TO BE REMOVED.

47:56.040 --> 47:58.372
<i>NOT A MAN?</i>

47:58.459 --> 48:00.791
NO, HARDLY A MAN.

48:00.878 --> 48:02.710
<i>HOW DID IT FEEL?</i>

48:13.599 --> 48:15.465
IT FELT...

48:17.311 --> 48:19.222
