48:19.313 --> 48:21.224
<i>MR. VOLLMER!</i>

48:21.315 --> 48:23.977
<i>WE ARE IMMORTAL!</i>

48:27.113 --> 48:29.650
YOU PETER VOLLMER?

48:29.740 --> 48:31.902
