FOR YOUR ARREST.

48:31.992 --> 48:35.235
CHARGE IS COMPLICITY
IN MURDER.

48:35.329 --> 48:37.912
VICTIM'S NAME
WAS NICHOLAS BLOSS.

48:37.998 --> 48:40.035
THAT SHOULD BE FAMILIAR TO YOU.

48:40.126 --> 48:41.833
THROW THAT GUN AWAY.

48:41.919 --> 48:43.830
WALK TOWARD US
WITH YOUR HANDS UP.

49:20.791 --> 49:23.704
THERE'S SOMETHING
VERY WRONG HERE.

49:23.794 --> 49:28.288
YOU'VE MADE A TERRIBLE MISTAKE.

49:28.382 --> 49:31.500
I'M MADE OUT OF STEEL.

49:31.594 --> 49:34.962
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND
THAT I'M MADE OUT OF STEEL?

49:43.397 --> 49:44.933
<i>WHERE WILL HE GO NEXT,</i>

49:45.024 --> 49:46.890
<i>THIS PHANTOM
FROM ANOTHER TIME,</i>

49:46.984 --> 49:49.316
<i>THIS RESURRECTED GHOST
OF A PREVIOUS NIGHTMARE--</i>

49:49.403 --> 49:52.145
<i>CHICAGO, LOS ANGELES,
MIAMI, FLORIDA,</i>

49:52.239 --> 49:54.526
<i>VINCENNES, INDIANA,
SYRACUSE, NEW YORK?</i>

49:54.617 --> 49:57.735
<i>ANYPLACE, EVERYPLACE,
WHERE THERE'S HATE,</i>

49:57.828 --> 50:00.411
<i>WHERE THERE'S PREJUDICE,
WHERE THERE'S BIGOTRY.</i>

50:00.498 --> 50:02.205
<i>HE'S ALIVE.</i>

50:02.291 --> 50:03.998
<i>HE'S ALIVE
SO LONG AS THESE EVILS EXIST.</i>

50:04.084 --> 50:06.166
<i>REMEMBER THAT
WHEN HE COMES TO YOUR TOWN.</i>

50:06.253 --> 50:08.039
<i>REMEMBER IT
WHEN YOU HEAR HIS VOICE</i>

50:08.130 --> 50:09.837
<i>SPEAKING OUT THROUGH OTHERS.</i>

50:09.924 --> 50:11.790
<i>REMEMBER IT
WHEN YOU HEAR A NAME CALLED,</i>

50:11.884 --> 50:13.249
<i>A MINORITY ATTACKED,</i>

50:13.344 --> 50:15.051
<i>ANY BLIND, UNREASONING ASSAULT</i>

50:15.137 --> 50:17.754
<i>ON A PEOPLE
OR ANY HUMAN BEING.</i>

50:17.848 --> 50:20.385
<i>HE'S ALIVE
BECAUSE THROUGH THESE THINGS,</i>

50:20.476 --> 50:22.513
<i>WE KEEP HIM ALIVE.</i>

